features: FASHIONABLE AND CUTE PATTERNS: 18 brand-new designed styles, inspired by cute and bright bouquets and leaves, each style is unique. Make storing your file folders full of fun, and the files are arranged more orderly and more personally.

INTIMATE DESIGNS: In the middle of these decorative file folders, we have added three folding lines, so you can fold it at will, and place files of corresponding thickness, which is more worry-free and faster.

HIGH-QUALITY MATERIALS: Made with 300 gsm paper, and the surface of the outer page is covered with a film to ensure that the folder is waterproof and not easy to tear. At the same time, the inner page is also covered with a matte film to ensure the color of the folder is long-lasting, won’t cause any smudges, to provide all-round protection of your files.
PRODUCT SIZE: 9.5 inches * 11 inches, suitable for US letter size documents.

VARIOUS APPLICATIONS: Suitable for all kinds of people, whether you are an office worker or a teacher or student. You can use it in any place and at any occasion, suitable for office, school, family, etc. We hope that our folders will add a new color to your life.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Jazz up your office!
reviews.reviewText: I bought these for a terrible subcontracting gig I had for the government. These folders have lasted longer than that miserable experience. They are of better quality than your standard manila folder and they just look….nice. Why not have pretty things to make our time at work a bit more enjoyable? These folders are worth it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I needed
reviews.reviewText: Excellent quality and beautiful prints. Will serve my 2024 needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and affordable
reviews.reviewText: These arrived in a timely manner. As expected. They're the most aesthetically appealing folders for the best price and stayed within the budget I was looking to spend. They seem to have ample weight and sturdiness to last a little while. I like that they have label tabs as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars File it under Pretty!
reviews.reviewText: This packet contains 18 beautiful files with 6 different designs. It’s perfect for a teacher, a home office, or quite frankly, anyone who wants a pretty sturdy file. These files are almost too pretty to be in a file drawer so I keep mine upright on my desk!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute, durable, but..
reviews.reviewText: These are super cute and very durable. However, they arrived a little dinged up on the corners. Also, it doesnt help that my mail delivery person bent them at a curve to put into my mailbox so I had to sit heavy books on top of them for several days prior to use to get them flat again. Will try to upload pics of the corners ASAP.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewText: These are very nice I like to change the colors to some of our files without being too obnoxious or bold

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are great folders. They're thick and strong enough to survive my backpack going from work to home. The size fits all of my papers and brochures. The colors are fun and vibrant. I would purchase again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars vibrant colors and sturdy build
reviews.reviewText: The beautiful and contrasting designs work together, but clearly stand out. It's cheery to pull out my work in such lovely folders...and helps keep me organized.
